        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <note>Following text structure is based on <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BLorient792">London, British Library, BL Oriental 792</ref>.</note>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="am" xml:id="Introduction">
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>በስመ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ይህ፡ ቀድሞ፡ በነቢያት፡ ዘመን፡ አልነበረም፡ ኋላ፡ ግን፡ ኢየሱስ፡
                            ክርስቶስ፡ ለሐዋርያት፡ ሲያስተምሕራቸው።</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                

                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="am" xml:id="Naakwetka">
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>ናሁ፡ እጽሕፍ፡ ትርጓሜ፡ ነአኵትከ፡ ዘተናገሩ፡ አባ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ ዘጋስጫ።</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                

                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="am" xml:id="Abuna">
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>ናሁ፡ እጽሕፍ፡ ትርጓሜ፡ አቡነ፡ ዘበሰመያት። አቡነ፡ በሰማያት፡ ምነው፡ በሰማያት፡ ያሰጠው፡ ያሉ፡ እንደሆን፡
                            እግዚአብሔር፡ በሰማይ፡ እንጅ፡ በምድርሰ፡ የለም።</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                

                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="am" xml:id="SalamaGabreel">
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>ናሁ፡ እጽሕፍ፡ ትርጓሜ፡ ሰላመ፡ ገብርኤል። በሰላመ፡ ገብርኤል፡ መልአክ፡ ማለት፡ እመቤቴሆይ፡ ገብርኤል፡ መልአክ፡
                            ሰላም፡ እንዳለሽ፡ እኔም፡ ባርያሽ፡ ሰላም፡ እልሻለሁ፡ ማለት፡ ነው።</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                

                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="am" xml:id="SalotaHaymanot" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5628CommCreed">
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>በስመ፡ ናሁ፡ ጸሎተ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ዘተናገሩ፡ በሀገረ፡ ኒቅያ፡ ፫ቱ፡ ፻ት፡ ፲ቱ፡ ወ፰ቱ፡ ርቱዓነ፡ ሃይማኖት፤
                            ጸሎተ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ማለት፡ ምን፡ ጊዜ፡ ተዠመረ፡ ያልኽ፡ እንደሆን፡ ኑማርያኖስ፡ የሚሉ፡ ንጉሠ፡ አንጾኪያ፡</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                

                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="am" xml:id="Hymn">
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>ሰላም፡ ለክሙ፡ አርእስተ፡ <add place="margin">ቅዱሳን፡</add> ዓበይት። ግዕዝክሙ፡ ይመስል፡ ግዕዘ፡
                            መላእክት። አበዊነ፡ መነኮሳት።</ab>
                    </div>
                    
                </div>

                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="am" xml:id="Dawit">
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>የዳዊትን፡ ታሪኩን፡ እንናገራለን፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ በገለጸልን፡ በምን፡ ምክንያት፡ ዳዊት፡ ይህን፡ ተናገረ፤ ነገር፡
                            ያለምክንያት፡ አይናገሩም።</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                

                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="am" xml:id="Hezekiah">
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>ታሪክ ይብል፡ አብድ፡ በልቡ፡ ባለ፡ ጊዜ፡ ታሪክ፡ ይህ፡ ነው።</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                

                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="am" xml:id="Zedekiah">
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>ታሪክ፡ ግፍዖሙ፡ ባለ፡ ጊዜ።</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                

                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="am" xml:id="Eleazar">
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>ታሪክ፡ እግዚኦ፡ ሰማዕነ፡ በዕዘኒነ፡ ባለ፡ ጊዜ፡ የመቃብያን፡ ታሪክ፡ ይተርኩታል።</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                

                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="am" xml:id="Abimelech">
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>ታሪክ፡ ለምንት፡ ይዜኃር፡ ዳዊት፡ ሸሽቶ፡ በሄደ፡ ጊዜ፡ ከሳኦል፡ አቤሜሌክ፡ የሚሉ፡ ሊቀ፡ ካህናት፡ ኖባማ፡
                            በሚሉ፡ ሀገር፡ ነበረ።</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                

                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="am" xml:id="Esther">
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>ታሪክ፡ የብቡ፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡ ባለ፡ ጊዜ፡ ታሪክ፡ ይህ፡ ነው፡ አስቴር፡ ይህን፡ አለች።</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                

                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="am" xml:id="Ps72">
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>የእግዚኦ፡ ኵነኔከ፡ ታሪክ፡ ይህ፡ ነው።</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                

                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="am" xml:id="Ps137">
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>ታሪክ፡ ውስተ፡ አፍላገ፡ ባቢሎን፡ ባለ፡ ጊዜ፡ የሚተረክ፡ ይህ፡ ነው።</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                

                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="am" xml:id="Prophets">
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>ታሪክ፡ የነቢያት፡ ይህ፡ ነው።</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                

                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="am" xml:id="Hannah"> </div>
                

                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="am" xml:id="Ps101"> </div>
                

                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="am" xml:id="Samuel1_15">
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>ነው፡ እስራእኤል፡ ያደኑት፡ ያማሌቅ፡ ንጉሥ፡ እንዴህ፡ ብሎ፡ አለው።</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                

                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="am" xml:id="Uriah">
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>የእግዚኦ፡ በመዓትከ፡ ታሪክ፡</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                

                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="am" xml:id="Absalom">
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>ታሪክ፡ እግዚኦ፡ አምላኪየ፡ ብከ፡ ተወከልኩ፡ ኢትግድፈኒ፡ ባለ፡ ጊዜ፡ የሚተረክ፡ ታሪክ፡ ይህ፡ ነው።</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                

                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="am" xml:id="Saints"> </div>
                

                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="am" xml:id="Saul"> </div>
                

                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="am" xml:id="Ps140">
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>ታሪክ፡ በተሰደደ፡ ጊዜ፡ አድኅነኒ፡ እግዚኦ፡ እምብእሲ፡ እኩይ፡ ብሎ፡ በዜህ፡ ዠመረ። አፈቅረከ፡ እግዚኦ፡
                            በኃይልየ። ብሎ፡ በማለት፡ ፈጸመ፡ </ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                

                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="am" xml:id="Amnon">
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>ታሪክ፡ እግዚኦ፡ ሚበዝኁ፡ ባለ፡ ጊዜ፤ የሚተረክ፡ ታሪክ፡ ይህ፡ ነው።</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                

                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="am" xml:id="Ps4">
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>ታሪክ፡ ሶበ፡ ጸዋዕክዎ፡ ባለ፡ ጊዜ፡ ይህ፡ ነው።</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                

                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="am" xml:id="Ps5">
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>ታሪክ፡ ቃልየ፡ አጽምዕ፡ እግዚኦ፡ ወልቡ፡ ጽራኅየ፡ ባለ፡ ጊዜ፡ የትሩፋን፡ ታሪክ፡ ይህ፡ ነው።</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                

                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="am" xml:id="Hanun">
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
